    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无需编程基础！人人都能打造属于自己的RPG！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《RPG Developer Bakin（写作“马琴”，以下简称Bakin）》是一款无需编程知识，任何人都能轻松上手的游戏制作工具。不仅可以制作各类 RPG，还能自由开发冒险游戏、动作游戏等多种类型的作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/493ee5e576d7cfd1fa306beb76283866.poster.avif?t=1769652143\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/493ee5e576d7cfd1fa306beb76283866.webm?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/493ee5e576d7cfd1fa306beb76283866.mp4?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >畅享游戏般的体验！功能强大而充满乐趣的地图编辑器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 地图是游戏的舞台。在Bakin中，设计地图就像用笔画图一样轻松便捷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在地图上设置各种元素，像是铺设草地，通过升降地面制作高低落差，再点缀些绿草繁花，以及房屋和家具。 不仅如此，地图上放置的物体均能自由缩放、旋转和变形，还能够放在任何位置。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，你还可以通过组合房屋、窗户和阳台等物体来定制你的专属模型哦。　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/0f8046e77b22864234e30eaeaaf8d696.poster.avif?t=1769652143\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/0f8046e77b22864234e30eaeaaf8d696.webm?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/0f8046e77b22864234e30eaeaaf8d696.mp4?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松打造印象深刻的场景！高度的视觉表现力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是模糊远景，还是调整整体光照氛围，Bakin的后处理特效都能帮你轻松实现丰富的视觉演出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，工具还内建多种高级功能，例如呈现手绘动画风格的“卡通渲染”、可隐藏图像局部的“遮罩功能”、以及可将2D素材贴附在场景中的“贴花”功能等，帮助你自由发挥创意，追求独属于你的视觉风格！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/e5f2bd549c0dea8181b6fb9119094af8.poster.avif?t=1769652143\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/e5f2bd549c0dea8181b6fb9119094af8.webm?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/e5f2bd549c0dea8181b6fb9119094af8.mp4?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排列面板即可！无需编程基础的事件编辑器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用Bakin制作游戏，并不需要编程知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要将“对话”“改变角色位置”“选项分支”等多种事件面板像拼图一样组合在一起，就能轻松完成事件制作，控制游戏流程。像是“加入队伍”“获得物品”“地图间移动”等常见事件，也提供了现成的模板，只需稍作修改即可直接使用，让你专注于剧情与创意设计！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/69586e2e31259a774c7a46f604687b04.poster.avif?t=1769652143\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/69586e2e31259a774c7a46f604687b04.webm?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/69586e2e31259a774c7a46f604687b04.mp4?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心修改界面设计！支援游戏创作的各式工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助Bakin的布局工具，你可以自由调整游戏画面的UI界面，打造符合风格的操作体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bakin还内建功能完善的数据库，可详细设定角色、物品等要素；配合动态演出的摄像机工具，更能呈现富有张力的场景。从系统架构到画面演出，Bakin提供多种功能强大的开发工具，全方位支持你的创作旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/b1f70cac84aa9aee6739b9d795dbd942.poster.avif?t=1769652143\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/b1f70cac84aa9aee6739b9d795dbd942.webm?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036640/extras/b1f70cac84aa9aee6739b9d795dbd942.mp4?t=1769652143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即刻开启游戏创作！一应俱全的丰富素材</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bakin内置大量游戏素材资源，包括角色、建筑等 2D/3D 图像、粒子特效、音效数据等，助你轻松搭建游戏舞台、烘托故事氛围。这些素材皆包含于工具本体，或可通过专属免费DLC获取。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还可选购额外的付费DLC，扩展素材种类，打造更加丰富多彩的游戏世界。当然，你也可以导入自制的3D模型、像素角色、插图与音效，实现个性化的创作体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，您也可以用 C# 创建插件，进一步扩展工具的功能。使用Bakin制作的游戏，无论是免费还是付费内容，皆可免版税发布与分发。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游玩示例游戏，确认软件是否你的世界，任你创造。心动不如行动，快使用Bakin将构想化作游戏吧！　</h2>",
